msgid "Configure [hosts](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Host_%28Unix%29) file on client workstation"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/45.tutorials/05.domains/dns_local_network.mdx:39
msgid ""
"Modifying hosts file should be done only if you cannot alter your box's DNS "
"or router, because hosts file will only impact the workstation where the "
"file was modified."
msgstr ""

